================================================================================
4. Development and validation tools (NOT redistributed)
================================================================================

BNGsim was developed and validated against several external tools that are NOT
redistributed with it — RoadRunner, AMICI, COPASI, BioNetGen's BNG2.pl /
run_network, and the SBML semantic test suite. Using them as reference oracles
imposes no redistribution obligation, but they are gratefully acknowledged, with
citations, in ACKNOWLEDGMENTS.md.


